<p class="eyebrow">API reference</p>
<h1>REST APIs for the VoiceTel platform.</h1>
<p class="lede">VoiceTel publishes OpenAPI specifications for every customer-facing API surface. Each reference is rendered from the spec, so the docs match the wire shape one-to-one.</p>

<p class="hero-actions">
	<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/docs/api/v2.2/credentials/">API credentials</a>
</p>

<section class="section-block">
